Package: mocap
Title: R interface to parsing and plotting Motion Capture files from the CMU Graphics Lab Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2017-08-17
Authors@R: person("Giora", "Simchoni", email = "gsimchoni@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package holds functions to easily parse motion capture ("mocap") files.
	Currently only ASF/AMC files are supported, and only those found in the
	Carnegie Mellon University Graphics Lab Motion Capture Database have been tested
URL: http://giorasimchoni.com/2017/08/08/2017-08-08-lambada-the-mocap-package/, http://mocap.cs.cmu.edu/
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: scatterplot3d
Suggests: animation
